xyz.fsgik.common.cache

接口 FsCache<K,V>


  • @ThreadSafe
public interface FsCache<K,V>
    Cache interface, is expected to thread-safe and doesn't support null value.

      • get

        @Nullable
V get(K key)
        Returns value associating with given key from this cache, return null if there is no entry for given key.
        参数:
        key - given key
        返回:
        value associating with given key from this cache

      • get

        @Nullable
V get(K key,
                 java.util.function.Function<? super K,? extends V> loader)
        Returns value associating with given key from this cache. If there is no entry for given key, a new value will be created by given loader.

        If the loader returns null, the null value will not be put and return null.

        参数:
        key - given key
        loader - given loader
        返回:
        value associating with given key from this cache, or created one
